ions based on user’s input or context,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and is commonly used to capture filtering decisions.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Suggestion chip is typically non-selected by default and can be tapped or clicked to apply the suggestion, streamlining input and enhancing usability.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Chips can show multiple interactive elements together in the same area, such as a list of selectable movie times, or a serie of email contacts.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Best suited for category-based filters that do not require additional visual elements.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSSuggestionChip/menuStyle(_:)":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudssuggestionchip\/menustyle(_:)","type":"topic","title":"menuStyle(_:)","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"menuStyle","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"S","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":">(","kind":"text"},{"text":"S","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"View","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI4ViewP","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip\/menuStyle(_:)","abstract":[],"kind":"symbol"}}}